    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Output comparison demonstrates NIH predictions within ±20% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for all evaluated conditions, satisfying the regulatory acceptance criterion. The CFD model is deemed credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
